ramonte in addition to his role at tbc bob is a board member for sterling bank corp parent company of sterling national bank a nyse company with over  billion in assets where he also serves on the audit and compensation committees community involvement living resources board member vice president nybdc charitable foundation chairman st peter’s hospital foundation chair leadership campaign executive and endowment committee teresian house audit and finance committee member union college executive committee member university at albany school of business advisory board chairman nybdc board member capital region sponsorascholar board member   just for fun when bob first worked for tbc in  he sat next to katie doran and john teevan who were staff accountants at the time bob enjoys being with his family including his eight grandchildren and spending time at his home in bolton landing he is also likely to be found with his friends either running playing golf travelling boating or playing water sports   professional credentials licensed certified public accountant cpa professional affiliations american institute of certified public accountants aicpa cpamerica international capital region chamber of commerce other team members john a chiaramonte ryan m smith robert l kind sarah p robinson john r teevan jr paula pierce robert h kind view firm directory  washington square albany ny  phone    fax     teal becker  chiaramonte all rights reserved  terms of use  contact us  emergency site by delphia consulting robert w lazar  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in robert w lazar board member at sterling bancorp view full profile are you robert w lazar claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view robert w lazars full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in robert w lazars network and community follow changes in robert w lazars employment and moneyinmotion connect with robert w lazar t