izations he serves on several committees of the new york bankers association he has been independent director of sterling bancorp since september   he served as a director of sterling national bank since september   he has received numerous awards such as small business executive of the year award from the capital district business review small business advocate of the year from empire state development corporation and entrepreneur of the year presented by the university at albany in addition to awards from schools and community groups for his various achievements he serves as a member of deans advisory board and member of school of business advisory council at school of business at the university at albany mr lazar is a certified public accountant and holds his bs in economics from the sage colleges and a ms in accounting from the university of albanyread full background corporate headquarters  rella boulevardmontebello new york united statesphone fax  board members memberships directornew york business development corporationpresentindependent director and director of sterling national banksterling bancorp education bs the sage collegesms university at albany other affiliations new york business development corporationsterling bancorp prior to merger with provident new york bancorpsterling national bankthe sage collegesuniversity at albanyschool of business at the university at albany annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation total annual cash compensationtotal calculated compensation request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationna