 vastly more powerful than the gravityb which we all know from our own everyday experience lazar further claimed that he was given introductory briefings describing the historical involvement by extraterrestrial beings with this planet for  years he claimed that the beings originated from the zeta retuculi    star system and are therefore referred to as zeta reticulans and are what many people refer to as the greys   w presented by robert s lazar on his commercial united nuclear website bob lazar writes in the aboutsection bob had previously worked at los alamos national laboratory specifically in the meson physics facility  involved with experiments using the  mile long linear particle accelerator critics have argued that the los alamos nuclear laboratory could not back up this claim the experimental laboratory denied ever having employed lazar investigative reporter george knapp however found bob lazars name among that of other scientists in the  los alamos phone book indicating lazar did work there as a technician in august  george knapp the reporter that first broke the story uncovered a w for robert lazar this slip represents payments after deductions for five days nonconsecutive working at the s base  lazar started at the end of december   and had only been at the base five times before the new year note at the top of the slip is a field reserved for the omb office of management and budget  note lazars employee number emaj compare the following badge issued to lazar by the security department at s lazar noted that he had majestic clearance this clearance level was  levels above q clearance at the bottom of the badge were the different sectors that this clearance would admit entrance to notice the s indication in the lower left corner the other three sectors are unfamiliar to lazar ds  etl  wx source mirror site for bobs website   address confirmation  bobs house in las vegas  to   county assessor record new mexico junior level national finalist cleveland middl